# NyayaSathi Environment Configuration

# === PRIORITY: Gemini API (Primary) ===
# Get your free Gemini API key from: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
# The app will try Gemini API first if this key is available

GEMINI_API_KEY=AIzaSyA-W6ZV8yLuwVj8tcfc8UmqUFAPx5GkfVk

# === FALLBACK: Ollama (Secondary) ===
# If Gemini API fails or key is not available, app falls back to Ollama
# Step 1: Install Ollama from https://ollama.ai
# Step 2: Run: ollama pull qwen2.5:3b
# Step 3: Run: ollama serve (keep this running in a terminal)
# Step 4: Start development server: node server.js

# For Ollama fallback (default):
OLLAMA_API_URL=http://localhost:11434/api/generate
OLLAMA_MODEL=qwen2.5:3b

# === PRIORITY SYSTEM ===
# The app automatically:
# 1. Tries Gemini API first (if GEMINI_API_KEY is set)
# 2. Falls back to Ollama if Gemini fails or key is missing
# 3. Works seamlessly in both local and production environments

